edifyarcane.title: Color: Trooper Black
edifyarcane.description: This eyeliner is everything it claims to be: insanely pigmented, super matte, and incredibly long-wearing. I have slightly hooded eyelids that can get oily, and this eyeliner doesn't budge all day long. The applicator is very different from the other KVD line, so it takes a bit of getting used to. The product dries super quickly, so you'll need to shake the container well to start and then dip a few times during application (takes me 2-3 times per eye). I find the formula super comfortable, and I'm impressed that it doesn't flake. Overall, it's my new go-to for cat eyes.
